## Key Design Choices

- **STL decomposition** used instead of classical additive decomposition — robust to the 2020 COVID anomaly
- **HDD/CDD degree-days** used instead of raw temperature — captures U-shaped demand-temperature relationship
- **168-hour LSTM look-back** — captures full weekly demand cycle including weekday/weekend pattern
- **Stepwise AIC search** (pmdarima) — covers p∈[0,6], d∈[0,2], q∈[0,6] efficiently
- **All lag features use shift ≥ 1** — prevents data leakage

